title: To My Boyfriend
lyrics: eegeotbwa nareul hanbeon chyeodabwa na jigeum eebbeu dago mal haebwa soljighi neoreul banha gehal saenggage nansaeng cheoeum chima do ibeosseo oojoobeun naeib sooreul bomyeonseo. moreun cheogmang seoriji marajweo eoje bon yeong hwaeh seo cheoreom nal ango ibmat choogoship dago mal haebwa nal bwa eonjena neoeui noonso ge a jigeun eorin nae mo seub saranghanda mal hagien eosaeghangeon sasilee ya hajiman na neoeui maeum soge seo eoneu saenga soo gyeoga dwe beorin geol nae saranghe je nooneul ddeun geo ya call me call me call call give a call nae modeun geol weon handa myeon neoehge joolgge gidaryeo watdeon naeui saran geun neoreul wihan geo ya call me call me call call give a call nae modeun geol naege saran ghi geoya ije jigeumee daero neoeui poomso ge nareul deryeo ga jweo nan ni ggeo ya neol sarang hae ee dae ro yeongweo nhi.
